    improvements (gh#amit9838/mousam#269).
  * feat: implement dynamic window view switching and centralize
    refresh logic (gh#amit9838/mousam#270).
  * Refactor Architecture, State Management, and UI Enhancements
    (gh#amit9838/mousam#271).
  * feat: introduce a logging system with configurable debug mode
    and log file management, improve const migration
    (gh#amit9838/mousam#272).
  * chore: update runtime to version 50 (gh#amit9838/mousam#276).
  * fix: remove mobile form factor metadata from appdata
    (gh#amit9838/mousam#277).

